Take output from preprocessing, and get ready for analysis. drop remaining out small outlier clusters (ex_16, ex_17, 17, 18), low quality clusters(ex_13), or mixed clusters (11,14) then split data into Rhombic lip-derived (RL) and ventricular zone-derived (VZ), rename clusters to the names found in the paper and come up with a color scheme.
